[FILE:330:descriptions/desc.single]
libepubgen is a library for generating documents in ePub format,
implementing librevenge document interfaces. It supports conversion of text
documents, presentations and vector drawings. Spreadsheets are not
supported. As these interfaces are used by multiple libraries, libepubgen
can be used to generate EPUB from many sources.


